{"tid":930394,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"竟然有人咳嗽會「把肺也咳出來」？","createTime":"2018-12-06T09:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T12:51:10.000Z","uid":1121,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"35a4d5dc37bb84bcdb203ce4219941a484289e16","tid":930394,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:46:46.000Z","msg":"身為一位胸腔科醫師，直覺上覺得不可能！<br />\n(當然，心中也閃過一些非常罕見的可能情況）<br />\n於是依媒體的報導去查一下「新英格蘭期刊」<br />\n果然是「假的」！<br />\n病人並沒有把肺或「支氣管樹」咳出來！<br />\n嚴格來說，也不算是「假新聞」，而是沒有把一個字弄懂，所造成的誤會！<br />\n這個字就是「Cast」就是我們一般說在打石膏的Cast！<br />\n也就是，咳出來的是「支氣管樹」的「鑄模」啦！<br />\n人家寫的是&rdquo;Cast of the Right Bronchial Tree&ldquo;<br />\n這「鑄模」怎麼來的呢？原來病人有使用抗凝血劑，造成支氣管內出血，這些血液在支氣管內「結塊」，形成「支氣管樹」的「鑄模」，然後被病人咳出來！<br />\n所以，被咳出來的是看起來「像支氣管樹」的血塊！不是支氣管樹啦！<br />\n臨床上，會咳出這麼完整又大塊的血塊，確實少見！<br />\n最近假新聞頻傳，希望媒體在報導聳動的議題前，能夠善䀆查證的義務 ，至少應該先詢問相關的專科醫師。<br />\n有沒有可以轉貼給相關媒體澄清一下呢？<br />\n新聞來源：<br />\n《不能只有我看到！ 男子狂咳 竟咳出整片支氣管樹》<br />\n2018-12-06 12:53聯合報 記者郭宣含╱即時報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://health.udn.com/health/story/5999/3521703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.udn.com%2Fhealth%2Fstory%2F5999%2F3521703&d=xfoDiEkTl4ylQGsgb%2F9wvcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ce6774f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://health.udn.com/health/story/5999/3521703</a><br />\n馬來西亞星洲日報（剛剛看，內文已經更正過來了）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1819091&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sinchew.com.my%2Fnode%2F1819091%E2%80%A6&d=xfoDiEkTl4ylQGsgb%2F9wvcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=94a088b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1819091&hellip;</a><br />\n醫學雜誌報導：<br />\n&rdquo;Cast of the Right Bronchial Tree&ldquo;<br />\nNovember 29, 2018<br />\nN Engl J Med 2018; 379:2151<br />\nDOI: 10.1056/NEJMicm1806493<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMicm180649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMicm180649&d=xfoDiEkTl4ylQGsgb%2F9wvcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0ba796ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMicm180649</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg12-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/47364291_2123128238016747_5350052898757672960_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg12-1.fna&amp;oh=597b62da5577e21371b88cdcc5d3dac2&amp;oe=5CB249CD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg12-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F47364291_2123128238016747_5350052898757672960_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg12-1.fna%26oh%3D597b62da5577e21371b88cdcc5d3dac2%26oe%3D5CB249CD&h=4f325e0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4da94be63d0db51aec9df6f1bd2dfe14aa9bca7","tid":930394,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5428eb6a2544d9bfa2f9f72bee539df35ef504","tid":930394,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"下？ 我睇電視明明見過有人真係成個肺咳左出黎嫁？乜假嫁？"},{"pid":"20b58426d88cf263b58ed99df6bfafbbc739cb1f","tid":930394,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a5ed060b1fb5a27308559a508b1a2a8c591985","tid":930394,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:22:34.000Z","msg":"啲血塊真係咁大舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個人竟然仲有命咳出黎"},{"pid":"5d318bec432c434292697cd678da0c7961f1ccc4","tid":930394,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a5ed060b1fb5a27308559a508b1a2a8c591985","tid":930394,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:22:34.000Z","msg":"啲血塊真係咁大舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/s